{"tid":2055042,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"星野源 ドラえもん(新番多啦A夢2019 OP) (廣東話改詞)","createTime":"2020-06-07T15:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T12:30:12.000Z","uid":125502,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9795197d95703c5721bece94a3cf060c4b088c89","tid":2055042,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:45:56.000Z","msg":"小妹第一次改詞，為香港人打氣<br />\n改編自「新番多啦A夢」於2019起使用的新OP<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c1WLnx2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc1WLnx2.png&h=d57c1b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡介：<br />\n香港人一路走來經歷風雨 心多渴望還原童真，有人陪伴在側成為小幫手，但現實殘酷，唯有夢境給予一絲歡樂空間，多得夢，打氣像啦啦隊，使情況成為A級般美好<br />\n<br />\n歌詞(廣東話)：<br />\n有些猜想不到的狀況 落到每天中小故事 <br />\n指尖班房抽屜小城市 夢裏跳出二次元 <br />\n<br />\n也有追趕不到那同輩 能量滿分的他也是 <br />\n天空灑出七彩過雲雨 存活在相同次元 <br />\n夢到救星來救援<br />\n<br />\n同寄居 同流淚 <span style=\"color: teal;\">(縱使他 鋼鐵機)</span><br />\n同渴望與一位機械 人挽手 再顫抖 <span style=\"color: teal;\">(仍會留下多少眼淚 大叫呼 喚勇敢)</span><br />\n呼喊心裡聲浪再高唱 <span style=\"color: teal;\">(高調去為勇士去呼喊) </span><br />\n全來到身邊 給一個擁抱<span style=\"color: teal;\">(前來快參加 出征戰爭吧)</span><br />\n全民就快出征 起勁再力拼<span style=\"color: teal;\">(全民快將都 守我這領土)</span><br />\n無論多麼小的微塵 勇救世界還原原來初心 <br />\n花光了青春 終歸會得勝 <span style=\"color: teal;\">(每日時光機飛奔幾千里)</span><br />\n逃避沒法得逞 風雨中覺醒 <span style=\"color: teal;\">(重遇那一天一切變完美)<br />\n</span><br />\n陪伴走過幾千公里 <br />\n沿途有你隨行齊心衝 多啦A夢<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">(與世間擁抱多得你<br />\n哆哆哆哆哆哆哆多得 多啦A夢)</span><br />\n<br />\n原OP：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/luKVC0saj5I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FluKVC0saj5I&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KceYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=b2d8ac7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/luKVC0saj5I</a><br />\n<strong>原曲 ドラえもん</strong><br />\n作詞・作曲・編曲・プロデュース / 星野源<br />\n<br />\n<strong>*黑色字為第一稿版本 <span style=\"color: teal;\">藍綠色字為第二個稿修改版</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歡迎畀意見</span>"},{"pid":"40b741ceee58fbf2b8938fc973085dcc92a50254","tid":2055042,"uid":142676,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:50:43.000Z","msg":"善心打破0回覆<br />\nBtw最憎多啦b夢"},{"pid":"6cac79f5d759ce3e2c3e2d9bb160cb1957b2b860","tid":2055042,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:53:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"11f386807057013d0cb10336031a7e450111973a","tid":2055042,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40b741ceee58fbf2b8938fc973085dcc92a50254","tid":2055042,"uid":142676,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:50:43.000Z","msg":"善心打破0回覆<br />\nBtw最憎多啦b夢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:55:04.000Z","msg":"多謝"},{"pid":"e4f426d9960534a9deca21aea01a9b543d1c171b","tid":2055042,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:17:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2942c8ffd61511e52a47af4f880c3bdfeae8daa0","tid":2055042,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e241d8e790cb1eb9a4e1d374496fa07d4512b167","tid":2055042,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:46:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f59f08b81b2620ed62319f8cd05c0e8325fe37db","tid":2055042,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2942c8ffd61511e52a47af4f880c3bdfeae8daa0","tid":2055042,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:30:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b1a0b5c558e